
 * this is a specific task which contributes to the building and
 managing of a project,

 * a goal may be a part of many phases,

 * a goal maybe executed after or before specific lifecycle,

 * creating a goal we have to specify in which phase we are going to execute that

 examples:

 * delete all target folder contents,

 * echo text messages for each phase of clean life cycle,
 - this is executed for clean phase of a clean life cycle,
 - <execution>
         <id>id.clean</id>
         <phase>clean</phase>
         <goals>
            <goal>run</goal>
         </goals>
         <configuration>
            <tasks>
               // print something in the console
               <echo>clean phase</echo>
            </tasks>
         </configuration>
      </execution>